{
  "_comment": [
    "IAM Execution Role Policy — Amazon Connect WebRTC Contact API",
    "",
    "Attach this inline policy to the IAM role assumed by the service:",
    "  • Lambda execution role   (aria-webrtc-api-exec-role)",
    "  • ECS task role           (aria-webrtc-api-task-role)",
    "",
    "Replace placeholder values before deploying:",
    "  <REGION>       e.g. eu-west-2",
    "  <ACCOUNT_ID>   12-digit AWS account ID",
    "  <INSTANCE_ID>  Amazon Connect instance ID (UUID)",
    "",
    "Authentication note:",
    "  This API uses AWS IAM SigV4 via AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity.",
    "  No Secrets Manager or Cognito permissions are required.",
    "  The Lambda Function URL (authType=AWS_IAM) or API Gateway",
    "  (authorizationType=AWS_IAM) validates the SigV4 signature;",
    "  this execution role only needs the Connect + CloudWatch actions.",
    "",
    "  connectparticipant:* is intentionally ABSENT — participant service",
    "  calls use the bearer ParticipantToken, not IAM credentials.",
    "",
    "References:",
    "  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/connect/latest/APIReference/API_StartWebRTCContact.html",
    "  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/lambda/latest/dg/urls-auth.html",
    "  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/connect/latest/adminguide/security-iam-amazon-connect-permissions.html"
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "ConnectWebRTCContacts",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "connect:StartWebRTCContact",
        "connect:StopContact",
        "connect:GetContactAttributes"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:connect:<REGION>:<ACCOUNT_ID>:instance/<INSTANCE_ID>/contact/*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "ConnectInstanceDescribe",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "connect:DescribeInstance"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:connect:<REGION>:<ACCOUNT_ID>:instance/<INSTANCE_ID>"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "CloudWatchLogs",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "logs:CreateLogGroup",
        "logs:CreateLogStream",
        "logs:PutLogEvents"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:logs:<REGION>:<ACCOUNT_ID>:log-group:/aws/lambda/aria-webrtc-api:*",
        "arn:aws:logs:<REGION>:<ACCOUNT_ID>:log-group:/ecs/aria-webrtc-api:*"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
